data.meta_description: Nate KochDecathlon - Mt. San Antonio College: Won the decathlon with a lifetime-best 6,939 points at the 2008 California Community College State Championship...
data.text:
Mt. San Antonio College: Won the decathlon with a lifetime-best 6,939 points at the 2008 California Community College State Championship ... Also a two-time Southern California decathlon champion ... Was a team captain and MVP.

High School: Four-year letterwinner at Temecula Valley High School ... Three-time team MVP ... Was the league champion in the long jump as a freshman ... Posted runner-up finishes in the long and high jump in 2003 ... Was a member of the 4x100 relay squad that ran a school record and won the league title ... Also left as the school record holder in the long jump, pole vault, 200m and 400m ... Lettered one year in water polo.

Personal: Majoring in psychology.
